            "type": "text",
            "text": "When evaluating embedding models for semantic search or retrieval-augmented generation, the choice between BGE M3 and OpenAI's offerings is critical. This post dives into BGE M3 vs openai, focusing on aspects that matter for production API teams, such as latency, accuracy, and deployment efficiency."
          }
